s="_slug__heading__yCwqF">FMI Morenci Mine Heap Leach Stacking Equipment</h1></div></div></div><div class="SingleProjectBuilder_contentWrapper__wDb_v _slug__section__1bDXK"><div class="SingleProjectBuilder_twoColumns__Wqgg_"><section class=""><div class=""><div class="TwoColumnsMedia_content__t5TpP TwoColumnsMedia_isFirstChild__jw8n0 SingleProjectBuilder_twoColContentClassName__Bsnq3"><div class="TwoColumnsMedia_textImage__LREFH"><div class="Container_container__sIK_T page-limit TwoColumnsMedia_container__a1LYV"><div class="TwoColumnsMedia_textImageRow2__b6kNT SingleProjectBuilder_row2ClassName__T4zDI"><div class="TwoColumnsMedia_infoImageWrapper__AiXdz"><div class="TwoColumnsMedia_infoImageCaption__r7c00"></div><figure class="TwoColumnsMedia_infoImage__AQZbh SingleProjectBuilder_imageClassName___fXRu"><span style="box-sizing:border-box;display:block;overflow:hidden;width:initial;height:initial;background:none;opacity:1;border:0;margin:0;padding:0;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;bottom:0;right:0"><img data-preload="false" sizes="(max-width: 768px) 100vw, 50vw" srcset="/_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcms.big-d.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F02%2Fcontent.jpg&amp;w=384&amp;q=75 384w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcms.big-d.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F02%2Fcontent.jpg&amp;w=640&amp;q=75 640w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcms.big-d.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F02%2Fcontent.jpg&amp;w=750&amp;q=75 750w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcms.big-d.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F02%2Fcontent.jpg&amp;w=828&amp;q=75 828w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcms.big-d.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F02%2Fcontent.jpg&amp;w=1080&amp;q=75 1080w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcms.big-d.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F02%2Fcontent.jpg&amp;w=1200&amp;q=75 1200w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcms.big-d.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F02%2Fcontent.jpg&amp;w=1920&amp;q=75 1920w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcms.big-d.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F02%2Fcontent.jpg&amp;w=2048&amp;q=75 2048w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcms.big-d.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F02%2Fcontent.jpg&amp;w=3840&amp;q=75 3840w" src="/_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcms.big-d.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F02%2Fcontent.jpg&amp;w=3840&amp;q=75" decoding="async" data-nimg="fill" style="position:absolute;top:0;left:0;bottom:0;right:0;box-sizing:border-box;padding:0;border:none;margin:auto;display:block;width:0;height:0;min-width:100%;max-width:100%;min-height:100%;max-height:100%;object-fit:cover"></span></figure></div><div class="TwoColumnsMedia_paragraph__AxfYk SingleProjectBuilder_paragraphClassName__kndab"><ul class="_slug__infoList__bUmOa"><li class="_slug__infoListItem__sRHOI"><div class="_slug__infoTitle__JjPbh">Market Sector</div><div class="_slug__infoValue__PkwDw">Industrial &amp; Mining</div></li><li class="_slug__infoListItem__sRHOI"><div class="_slug__infoTitle__JjPbh">Project Location</div><div class="_slug__infoValue__PkwDw">Morenci, Arizona</div></li><li class="_slug__infoListItem__sRHOI"><div class="_slug__infoTitle__JjPbh">Company</div><div class="_slug__infoValue__PkwDw">Construction</div></li><li class="_slug__infoListItem__sRHOI"><div class="_slug__infoTitle__JjPbh">Description</div><div class="TwoColumnsMedia_infoValueDescription__9ljSr Paragraph_paragraph__7JSG3">Construction of three ramp super-portable conveyors for Terra Nova Technologies. The site is located at the Freeport-McMoRan Morenci Mine and supports building mine leach stockpiles to produce copper. The Morenci Mine uses portable ore conveying and stacking equipment to progressively build their leaching stockpiles. These stockpiles are vital components of the mining process, and their efficient management directly impacts copper production. Big-D Heavy Industrial was meticulous in constructing the conveyors, self-performing structural and mechanical assemblies. Each conveyor has a length of over 250 feet and is track-mounted to facilitate their mobility, allowing them to traverse ramps and navigate across stockpiles with ease.</div></li></ul></div></div></div></div></div></div></section></div></div><hr class="_slug__separator__uA2ej"><div class="_slug__relatedProjects__6A3vF _slug__section__1bDXK"><h2 class="_slug__subHeading__nXkC_">Related Projects</h2><ul class="_slug__flexWrapper__LnRZ0"><li class="ProjectCard_item__6wOvS ProjectCard_lightVariant__tlsS7" style="opacity: 1; transform: none;"><a class="ProjectCard_card__C5E2y" rel="" href="#"><div class="ProjectCard_imageSection__Ne8u5"><div class="ProjectCard_imageWrapper__inUKt"><figure class="ProjectCard_image__u21cd"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; display: block; overflow: hidden; width: initial; height: initial; background: none; opacity: 1; border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; position: absolute; inset: 0px;"><img alt="Sunroc Corporation Bluffdale Office &amp; Manufacturing Facility" data-preload="false" src="/_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcms.big-d.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F01%2FSunroc_BluffdaleDJI_0218_BLAKELY_SH.jpg&amp;w=3840&amp;q=75" decoding="async" data-nimg="fill" class="ProjectCard_imageTag__746su" style="position: absolute; inset: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; border-width: medium; border-style: none; border-color: currentcolor; border-image: none; margin: auto; display: block; width: 0px; height: 0px; min-width: 100%; max-width: 100%; min-height: 100%; max-height: 100%; object-fit: cover;" sizes="(max-width: 768px) 100vw, 50vw" srcset="/_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcms.big-d.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F01%2FSunroc_BluffdaleDJI_0218_BLAKELY_SH.jpg&amp;w=384&amp;q=75 384w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcms.big-d.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F01%2FSunroc_BluffdaleDJI_0218_BLAKELY_SH.jpg&amp;w=640&amp;q=75 640w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcms.big-d.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F01%2FSunroc_BluffdaleDJI_0218_BLAKELY_SH.jpg&amp;w=750&amp;q=75 750w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcms.bi